    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-02-12T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-02-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="143" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d143">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rio de
                                    Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-02-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 12, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.
                            (Received February 12.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson telegraphs that the insurgents on the preceding Saturday landed
                        at Nitcheroy and were repulsed, returning to their ships after an
                        engagement, in the course of which both sides lost heavily and Admiral da
                        Gama received wounds in his arm and breast.</p>
            </div>
